{"tid":354374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[肥婆掉眼淚]興德校歌 獨家試唱","createTime":"2017-08-10T11:36:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T05:19:15.000Z","uid":70786,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca615ed7d0dd27bd02c57ddc7b3128b7c3bf0eb7","tid":354374,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T11:36:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/100018_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F100018_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b8e13e80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n肥婆掉眼淚<br />\n原曲:如何掉眼淚<br />\n曲:陳輝陽<br />\n<br />\n嫌吃下M記都不夠味　狂點新地茄醬都不顧忌<br />\n去公廁釋放一噸廢氣　放一篤　超濕屁<br />\n<br />\n肥婆佢係怕胖怕到要死　偏要學人獨行食拖肥<br />\n入獄都不會避忌　連狂喫(jaak3)西餅亦未見喘氣<br />\n<br />\n*肥婆掉眼淚   話興德不欣賞佢　臭八婆自我嘉許　<br />\n最愛校裏的批鬥　又被爆收稅<br />\n肥婆掉眼淚　校董心知她不對　這阿萍極缺德  話一堆新聞屈佢<br />\n谷一殼淚　離場時仍然獨吃兩舊　揚長在記招去<br />\n<br />\n連副校也被傷風撲鼻　萍姐只顧偏愛餅香氣味<br />\n最好有朱奶芝士送佢　刺激多些分泌<br />\n<br />\n悠然繼續吃飯吃到便意起　谷屁谷到只有鬧風紀<br />\n大便不出最驟忌　仍狂喫芝士便會谷鬼氣<br />\n<br />\n肥婆係有罪　廿打西餅吞咗佢    叫阿SIR代佢抽水　<br />\n最愛是老師請假　又獨吃餅碎<br />\n<br />\nWoo~~~ 先生一致故意的連累<br />\n欲脫罪   但沒法騙取<br />\n不想坐一世連同你檢舉 Ah~~~<br />\n<br />\nRepeat *<br />\n<br />\n在課室一堆餅碎　心知有罪　回頭時連肥胖稅八萬　同回贈騙款裏</blockquote>"},{"pid":"22988501d03b3f203e8e03c8ebd855914a7aca0d","tid":354374,"uid":42217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T11:37:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f0a34e5ec9620f2b43bea25c0c468b5061c480","tid":354374,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T11:40:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc2440c4ccd4829cef43b8c56a263eba70986b45","tid":354374,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T11:45:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你確定啱音？</blockquote><br />\n肥絲改字唔夠<br />\n連音都改埋<br />\n請賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8618922f0d5af3ba4017eac2543aa1d8e1f6c33","tid":354374,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T11:48:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc33e172896fcbf6b190951d8085637efa60e2e6","tid":354374,"uid":46042,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T11:52:30.000Z","msg":"[quote]你確定啱音？[/quote<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">蒸翼老師評分。 <br />\n<br />\n你太肥 c+</span></span>"},{"pid":"5ad09608f6f46ae70f68242ccf66814b996332d5","tid":354374,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T11:58:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你確定啱音？</blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">蒸翼老師評分。 <br />\n<br />\n你太肥 c+</span></span></blockquote><br />\n同類<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016e42d55c0fe1087a2573c2a791bf2fddb2a1a1","tid":354374,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T12:01:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e1ba0d6d5a2a3f2cabc5abec626e72c57b7473d","tid":354374,"uid":109393,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T12:02:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>嫌吃下M記都不夠味　狂點新地茄醬都不顧忌</blockquote><br />\n原詞：<br />\n<blockquote>如吃掉芥辣都不刺鼻　洋蔥不再釋放傷感氣味</blockquote><br />\n唱成：<br />\n嫌吃下<span style=\"color: red;\">em3技</span>都不夠味<br />\n狂<span style=\"color: red;\">dim1</span>新<span style=\"color: red;\">dei3 ke1</span>醬都<span style=\"color: red;\">bat2</span>顧忌<br />\n<br />\n淨係頭一行都六個唔啱音就咪撚獻醜啦</blockquote><br />\n關你撚事咩你老母俾狗屌"},{"pid":"cf0590271c672ddff9a35a0cee86b4cd2afbbd5e","tid":354374,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T12:03:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54a3a35bec5e2cee54896135121c3559517d0853","tid":354374,"uid":13305,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re